{"id":641321,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/【最美逆行】-中国有你们真好/","date":"2020-04-10T22:32:59Z","modified":"2020-04-11T00:15:12Z","title":"【最美逆行】 “中国有你们真好”","content":"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641329\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.23.13.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"133\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.23.13.png 596w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.23.13-300x80.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>急诊向日葵艾芬：一位成都的退休优秀教师，专程来到武汉，自费租房子，想为需要的孩子义务做心理辅导。她说：之前在汶川地震曾经帮助过失去亲人的孩子，这次也想用自己的专业知识来帮助更多的孩子，不然自己活得不心安。她给我朗诵了几首中英文诗歌，还给我送了鲜花。感动。 ​​​​</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641328\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.22.59.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"686\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.22.59.png 497w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.22.59-219x300.png 219w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641323\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.21.10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"588\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.21.10.png 497w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.21.10-255x300.png 255w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641324\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.21.30.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"616\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.21.30.png 551w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Screenshot-2020-04-10-15.21.30-243x300.png